vala-lint
------------------------------------------
Small command line tool and library for checking Vala code files for
code-style errors. Based on the elementary Code-Style guidelines.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.5-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.87.0-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.87.0-1
  libjson-glib1.0_0-1.4.2-1
  libvala-linter1.0-devel-0.1.0+git20250803-1bl1
  libvala-linter1.0_1.0.0-0.1.0+git20250803-1bl1
  libvala0.56-devel-0.56.18-1
  libvala0.56_0-0.56.18-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cygport-0.37.5-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.87.0-1
  libjson-glib1.0-devel-1.4.2-1
  libvala0.56-devel-0.56.18-1
  meson-1.4.2-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1
  vala-0.56.18-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/vala-lang/vala-lint

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/vala-lang/vala-lint.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack vala-lint-0.1.0+git20250803-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./vala-lint-0.1.0+git20250803-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/vala-lint-0.1.0+git20250803-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/vala-lint-0.1.0+git20250803-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libvala-linter1.0_1.0.0-0.1.0+git20250803-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libvala-linter1.0-devel-0.1.0+git20250803-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/vala-vala-linter1-0.1.0+git20250803-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(vala-lint)
  /usr/bin/io.elementary.vala-lint.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/vala-lint.README
  /usr/share/doc/vala-lint/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/vala-lint/README.md

(libvala-linter1.0_1.0.0)
  /usr/bin/cygvala-linter-1.0-1.0.0.dll

(libvala-linter1.0-devel)
  /usr/include/vala-linter-1.0/vala-linter.h
  /usr/lib/libvala-linter-1.0.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/vala-linter-1.pc

(vala-vala-linter1)
  /usr/share/vala/vapi/vala-linter-1.vapi

